align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt; font-size:13.0pt; padding:0in\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">1</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-1 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"303\" name=\"question-1\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"YES\">YES</option><option value=\"NO\">NO</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">Networking is not a modern idea.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt; font-size:13.0pt; padding:0in\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">2</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-2 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"304\" name=\"question-2\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"YES\">YES</option><option value=\"NO\">NO</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">Networking is worn like a badge exclusively in the business world.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt; font-size:13.0pt; padding:0in\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">3</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-3 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"305\" name=\"question-3\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"YES\">YES</option><option value=\"NO\">NO</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">People fall into two basic categories.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt; font-size:13.0pt; padding:0in\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">4</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-4 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"306\" name=\"question-4\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"YES\">YES</option><option value=\"NO\">NO</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">A person who shares knowledge and friends makes a better networker than one who does not.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt; font-size:13.0pt; padding:0in\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">5</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-5 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"307\" name=\"question-5\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"YES\">YES</option><option value=\"NO\">NO</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\">The classic networker is physically strong and generally in good health.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><