ion\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<caption>Keyword Table</caption>\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Words in Question</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Similar words in passage</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#d35400;\"><strong>Get angry</strong></span>, <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>live longer&nbsp;</strong></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>These patients get sick faster and they <span style=\"color:#e74c3c;\"><strong>die sooner</strong></span> than people who <span style=\"color:#d35400;\"><strong>became angry</strong></span> at their cancer and fight the disease.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This paragraph explains about some traits that help vitims of cancer recover from their illness. The last sentence talk about becoming angry at victim\'s cancer themeself will help live longer. So, <strong>heading i</strong> is the right answer</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">5. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-5 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"11\" name=\"question-5\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"i\">i</option><option value=\"ii\">ii</option><option value=\"iii\">iii</option><option value=\"iv\">iv</option><option value=\"v\">v</option><option value=\"vi\">vi</option><option value=\"vii\">vii</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Paragraph E</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-5 explain-area-11\" data-qnumber=\"11\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"4\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 5 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">iv</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-11\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-11\" data-qnumber=\"11\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"4\" onclick=\"showExplanation(11,5)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Which one <strong>causes</strong> which? &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>getting <strong>cancer may cause</strong> people to develop a <strong>cancer-prone personality.</strong></p>\n\n			<p>there is no proof that having a <strong>cancer-prone personality causes cancer.</strong></p>\n\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>this paragraph clearly talks about the relationship of cancer-prone personality and cancer, which one causes which?</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>heading iv</strong> is the correct answer</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n', 5, 1, 4, 3, 1, '2017-10-26 16:43:42', '2017-11-15 09:16:20');
