yle=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>vi &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Political change obstructs progress in urban planning</b></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>vii &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; An urban plan to reduce traffic</b></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">1.</span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-1 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"18\" name=\"question-1\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"i\">i</option><option value=\"ii\">ii</option><option value=\"iii\">iii</option><option value=\"iv\">iv</option><option value=\"v\">v</option><option value=\"vi\">vi</option><option value=\"vii\">vii</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Paragraph&nbsp; A</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">2.</span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-2 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"19\" name=\"question-2\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"i\">i</option><option value=\"ii\">ii</option><option value=\"iii\">iii</option><option value=\"iv\">iv</option><option value=\"v\">v</option><option value=\"vi\">vi</option><option value=\"vii\">vii</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Paragraph&nbsp; B</span></span></span></p>\