argin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>C. It is better to change the bad eating habits.</b></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>D.&nbsp; A bad diet is harmful.</b></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>E. People differ from each other.</b></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>F. Enough proteins, vitamins and minerals are provided in a good diet.</b></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>G. We do not need vitamin pills. </b></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">1. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-1 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"43\" name=\"question-1\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option><option value=\"F\">F</option><option value=\"G\">G</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Section I </span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-1 explain-area-43\" data-qnumb