howExplanation(66,2)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>This is <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>best</strong></span> if you <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>like surfing the Web.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Broadband Internet connections</strong></span>&nbsp;and telephones...</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>You have to brainstorm that web related to the internet. Because in this paggase, there is no information about web, only paragraph A give information about broadband internet connection, it means that this house would be good for surfing the web.</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>paragraph A</strong> is the correct answer of this question.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>3 </b></span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-3 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"67\" name=\"question-3\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Of the College residences, this has the fewest students.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-3 explain-area-67\" data-qnumber=\"67\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"5\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 3 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">D</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-67\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-67\" data-qnumber=\"67\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"5\" onclick=\"showExplanation(67,3)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Of the College residences, this has the <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>fewest students</strong></span>.</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>...and housing&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>120 students&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>Just make comparison between those hose, we can see that Glencarrick house has the fewest students.</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>paragraph D</strong> is the correct answer.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><strong>4</strong>&nbsp;</span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-4 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"125\" name=\"question-4\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option></select>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">This is a option offered by the College</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-4 explain-area-125\" data-qnumber=\"125\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"5\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 4 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">D</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-125\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-125\" data-qnumber=\"125\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"5\" onclick=\"showExplanation(125,4)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>This is a option <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>offered</strong></span> <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>by the College&nbsp;</strong></span> &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Rooms are <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>allocated</strong></span> <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>by the College Accommodation Service</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This rooms are allocated by the college, means that this rooms are offered by the college.</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>paragraph D</strong> is the correct answer.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>5 </b></span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-5 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"69\" name=\"question-5\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">You have to organise parking a year at a time.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-5 explain-area-69\" data-qnumber=\"69\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"5\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 5 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">B</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-69\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-69\" data-qnumber=\"69\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"5\" onclick=\"showExplanation(69,5)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>You have to <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>organise parking a year at a time.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Parking is available</strong></span> with permits costing £90 <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>for the academic year.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>The last sentece of paragraph B gives information about this. Only Student Village requires this action.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>6 </b></span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-6 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"70\" name=\"question-6\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">This accommodation does not belong to the College.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-6 explain-area-70\" data-qnumber=\"70\" data-qorder=\"6\" data-type-question=\"5\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 6 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">D</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-70\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-70\" data-qnumber=\"70\" data-qorder=\"6\" data-type-question=\"5\" onclick=\"showExplanation(70,6)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>This accommodation does <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>not belong to the College.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><strong>GLENCARRICK HOUSE</strong>&nbsp;-&nbsp;a <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>privately-owned&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This house is a privately-owned.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>7 </b></span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-7 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"71\" name=\"question-7\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Here you definitely do not have your own bathroom.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-7 explain-area-71\" data-qnumber=\"71\" data-qorder=\"7\" data-type-question=\"5\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 7 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">C</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-71\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-71\" data-qnumber=\"71\" data-qorder=\"7\" data-type-question=\"5\" onclick=\"showExplanation(71,7)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Here you definitely <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>do not have your own bathroom.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Eighteen rooms per floor with <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>communal </strong></span>kitchens, lounges, <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>bathrooms</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>Communal means belonging to or used by a group of people rather than one single person.</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>paragraph C</strong> is the correct answer for this question.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n', 7, 3, 5, 3, 1, '2017-10-27 11:19:43', '2017-11-15 14:02:38');
