class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-72\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-72\" data-qnumber=\"72\" data-qorder=\"1\" data-type-question=\"5\" onclick=\"showExplanation(72,1)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" order=\"1\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>It is <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>awarded on results</strong></span> obtained in the <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>SCE exam</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>....<span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>to the three most outstanding</strong></span> State Certificate of Education <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>(SCE) students</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>Scanning for SCE, you can find the information about it in category B &amp; E. However, category E indicates that this scholarship is not awarded based on SEC results.</p>\n\n<p>So, B is the correct answer</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>2 </b></span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-2 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"73\" name=\"question-2\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option><option value=\"F\">F</option><option value=\"G\">G</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">It is only available to students from the College\'s overseas branch.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-2 explain-area-73\" data-qnumber=\"73\" data-qorder=\"2\" data-type-question=\"5\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 2 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">A</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-73\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-73\" data-qnumber=\"73\" data-qorder=\"2\" data-type-question=\"5\" onclick=\"showExplanation(73,2)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>It is only available to students from the <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>College\'s overseas branch.</strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>One scholarship of A$2000 for the most outstanding students entering the Foundation Studies Program from each of the following countries: <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Singapore, Malaysia and Thailand. </strong></span>An additional six scholarships are available for students from <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>other countries</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This scholarship is offered only to some asian countries such as Singapore, Malaysia and Thailand....</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>3 </b></span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-3 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"74\" name=\"question-3\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option><option value=\"F\">F</option><option value=\"G\">G</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">It is not offered every year</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-3 explain-area-74\" data-qnumber=\"74\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"5\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 3 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">F</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-74\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-74\" data-qnumber=\"74\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"5\" onclick=\"showExplanation(74,3)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>It is <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>not offered every year&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>his scholarship <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>is offered every second year...</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This category scholarship is offered every second years, not every year.</p>\n\n<p>So, F is the correct answer</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>4 </b></span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-4 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"75\" name=\"question-4\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option><option value=\"F\">F</option><option value=\"G\">G</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Students need to apply for it</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-4 explain-area-75\" data-qnumber=\"75\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"5\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 4 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">E</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-75\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-75\" data-qnumber=\"75\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"5\" onclick=\"showExplanation(75,4)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Students <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>need to apply</strong></span> for it&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Note that applicants <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>need to apply for this scholarship</strong></span> on the Bramley College International Scholarship Application Form.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>Only this category requires students to apply. Others will award based on the result of previous semester or a specific certificate.</p>\n\n<p>So, E is the correct answer.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>5 </b></span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-5 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"76\" name=\"question-5\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option><option value=\"F\">F</option><option value=\"G\">G</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">It is offered twice each year</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-5 explain-area-76\" data-qnumber=\"76\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"5\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 5 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">A</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-76\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-76\" data-qnumber=\"76\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"5\" onclick=\"showExplanation(76,5)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>It is offered <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>twice each year&nbsp; &nbsp; </strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>These scholarships are offered <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>on two dates</strong></span>, to students <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>in the March</strong></span> and <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>June </strong></span>intakes of the program</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>These scholarships are offered on two dates - means twice a year.</p>\n\n<p>Category A is the correct answer.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>6 </b></span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-6 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"77\" name=\"question-6\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option><option value=\"F\">F</option><option value=\"G\">G</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">It pays 100% of the student\'s tuition fees</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-6 explain-area-77\" data-qnumber=\"77\" data-qorder=\"6\" data-type-question=\"5\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 6 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">F</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-77\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-77\" data-qnumber=\"77\" data-qorder=\"6\" data-type-question=\"5\" onclick=\"showExplanation(77,6)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>It pays <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>100% of the student\'s tuition fees</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>One <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>full-fee scholarship</strong></span>&nbsp;to the most outstanding student&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>It is clear that this is full-fee scholarship (means 100% fee).</p>\n\n<p>As the result, F is the correct answer.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>7 </b></span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-7 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"78\" name=\"question-7\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"A\">A</option><option value=\"B\">B</option><option value=\"C\">C</option><option value=\"D\">D</option><option value=\"E\">E</option><option value=\"F\">F</option><option value=\"G\">G</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">It provides 50% of one year\'s fees</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-7 explain-area-78\" data-qnumber=\"78\" data-qorder=\"7\" data-type-question=\"5\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 7 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">G</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-78\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-78\" data-qnumber=\"78\" data-qorder=\"7\" data-type-question=\"5\" onclick=\"showExplanation(78,7)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>It provides <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>50% of </strong></span><span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>one year\'s fees&nbsp;</strong></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Four&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>half-fee scholarships</strong></span>&nbsp;to outstanding students of&nbsp; Bramley College\'s Singapore campus<span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong> for the final year </strong></span>of the two-year Certificate.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>Half-fee means 50%. The remaining scholarship is not offer 50%.</p>\n\n<p>So, G is the correct answer.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n', 7, 4, 5, 3, 1, '2017-10-27 11:23:14', '2017-11-15 14:12:54');
