r 2 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">B</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-129\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-129\" data-qnumber=\"129\" data-qorder=\"2\" data-type-question=\"6\" onclick=\"showExplanation(129,2)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>However, ecotourism can <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>cause problems </strong></span>when:</p>\n\n			<p><strong>C:</strong>&nbsp;communities <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>do not have the funds to improve local facilities.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>ecotourism operations occasionally <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>fail to live up to conservation ideals</strong></span>.</p>\n\n			<p>The <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>environment may suffer</strong></span> because local communities are <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>unable to meet these infrastructure demands..</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>There is no information about answer A &amp; C. Answer B is the correct one. You can easily find the information in highlighted sentences</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\">&nbsp;</p>\n', 2, 2, 6, 3, 1, '2017-11-06 14:56:55', '2017-11-15 14:37:30');
