\" times=\"\">Relics of early civilization</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>D</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-1 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"130\" name=\"question-1\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"D\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">9 adult males, 7 adult females and 16 children</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-1 explain-area-130\" data-qnumber=\"130\" data-qorder=\"1\" data-type-question=\"6\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 1 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">B</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-130\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-130\" data-qnumber=\"130\" data-qorder=\"1\" data-type-question=\"6\" onclick=\"showExplanation(130,1)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>What </strong></span>did <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>archaeologists in southern Germany discover</strong></span>?</p>\n\n			<p>B: <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>Graveyard containing 34 skeletons</strong><b><strong>.&nbsp;</strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</b></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>archaeologists in southern Germany</strong></span> <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>discovered </strong></span>a mass <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>grave containing 34 skeletons</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;A is not the right answer, because that is 34 dead human skeletons, not animals</p>\n\n<p><strong>B </strong>is the correct answer, you can find information in highlighted sentence.</p>\n\n<p>C is incorrect because there is no information that this skeletons are the relics of early civilization</p>\n\n<p>D is also wrong, because archaelogists found dead skeletons, but this answer does not mention about this fact.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n	<li style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>Why did scientists suggested that those people were killed whilst running away?</b></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>A</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-2 \" data-qnumber=\"131\" name=\"question-2\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"A\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Their skeletons showed signs of fatal trauma</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>B</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-2 \" data-qnumber=\"131\" name=\"question-2\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"B\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">There were 16 children</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>C</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-2 \" data-qnumber=\"131\" name=\"question-2\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"C\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">During that period organised group violence was very frequent</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>D</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-2 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"131\" name=\"question-2\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"D\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Their skeletons didn\'t show any signs of defensive wounds</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-2 explain-area-131\" data-qnumber=\"131\" data-qorder=\"2\" data-type-question=\"6\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 2 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">D</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-131\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-131\" data-qnumber=\"131\" data-qorder=\"2\" data-type-question=\"6\" onclick=\"showExplanation(131,2)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Why did scientists suggested that those people were <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>killed whilst running away</strong></span>?</p>\n\n			<p>D: <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>Their skeletons didn\'t show any signs of defensive wounds</strong></span>.</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>None of them showed any signs of defensive wounds</strong></span>, suggesting <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>they were killed whilst running away.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>Answer A, B, C give the right information about those skeletons, however, they are not the key reason for this question.</p>\n\n<p>In highlighted sentence, we can find answer for this question - that is noe of defensive wounds.</p>\n\n<p>So, D is the correct answer.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n	<li style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>Why do human beings fight, according to the article?</b></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>A</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-3 \" data-qnumber=\"132\" name=\"question-3\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"A\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Because they have been fighting wars for thousands of years</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>B</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-3 \" data-qnumber=\"132\" name=\"question-3\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"B\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Because chimpanzees, who are humans\' closest relatives, engage in warfare</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>C</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-3 \" data-qnumber=\"132\" name=\"question-3\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"C\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Because humans inherited predilection for warfare from their ape-like ancestors</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>D</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-3 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"132\" name=\"question-3\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"D\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Because fighting is their inbuilt instinct</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-3 explain-area-132\" data-qnumber=\"132\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"6\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 3 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">C</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-132\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-132\" data-qnumber=\"132\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"6\" onclick=\"showExplanation(132,3)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Why do human beings fight, according to the article?:</p>\n\n			<p>C: Because <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>humans inherited predilection for warfare from their ape-like ancestors.&nbsp;</strong></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>That suggests we have <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>inherited our predilection for warfare from our ape-like ancestors</strong></span>. But not everyone agrees that warfare is inbuilt.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>The information in answer A &amp; B are not wrong, however, this is the main reason for this question.</p>\n\n<p>In the last sentences of this paragraph, we can find out the main reason, and C is the right answer.</p>\n\n<p>Answer D is wrong, because \"not everyone agrees that warfare is inbuilt\".</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<ol start=\"4\">\n	<li style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>Which of the following phrases best describes the main aim of the Reading Passage?</b></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>A</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-4 \" data-qnumber=\"133\" name=\"question-4\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"A\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">To describe fighting among different species</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>B</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-4 \" data-qnumber=\"133\" name=\"question-4\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"B\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">To intoduce principles of contemporary archaeology and its application</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>C</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-4 \" data-qnumber=\"133\" name=\"question-4\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"C\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">To introduce some relics of humans\' warfare for further discussion whether violence is innate or not</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>D</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-4 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"133\" name=\"question-4\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"D\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">To suggest ways of interperting humans\' violence</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-4 explain-area-133\" data-qnumber=\"133\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"6\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 4 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">C</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-133\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-133\" data-qnumber=\"133\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"6\" onclick=\"showExplanation(133,4)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>To introduce some relics of <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>humans\' warfare</strong></span> for <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>further discussion</strong></span> whether violence <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>is innate or not</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Those information is all provided in this passage&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This is no clear information for answer A and B</p>\n\n<p>For answer D, it is also not clear in this paragraph, because this paragraph only give explaination of origin of hunam\'s violence, not the ways.</p>\n\n<p>C is the correct answer.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n', 4, 3, 6, 3, 1, '2017-11-06 15:03:48', '2017-11-15 14:47:41'),
(25, 'Practice 4', 2, '<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">A new &lsquo;super-Earth&rsquo; has been discovered that could have a life-supporting climate and water. The planet, given the catchy name HD 40307g, was discovered in a multi-world solar system 42 light years from the Sun and lies at exactly the right distance from its star to allow liquid surface water. It orbits well within the star&#39;s &ldquo;habitable&rdquo; or &ldquo;Goldilocks&rdquo; zone - the region where temperatures are neither too hot nor too cold to sustain life.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Professor Hugh Jones, from the University of Hertfordshire said: &ldquo;The longer orbit of the new planet means that its climate and atmosphere may be just right to support life. Just as Goldilocks liked her porridge to be neither too hot nor too cold but just right, this planet or indeed any moons that is has lie in an orbit comparable to Earth, increasing the probability of it being habitable.&rdquo; The &lsquo;super earth&rsquo; is one of six planets believed to circle the dwarf star HD 40307 in the constellation Pictor. All the others are located outside the habitable zone, too close to their parent star to support liquid water.</span></span></span></p>\n', '\n                                    \n                                    \n                                    \n                                    <p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">A new ‘super-Earth’ has been discovered that could have a life-supporting climate and water. The planet, given the catchy name HD 40307g, was discovered in a multi-world solar <span class=\"answer-highlight highlight-1 hidden-highlight\" data-timestamp=\"1510732223297\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 123);\" data-highlighted=\"true\" data-qnumber=\"134\" id=\"hl-answer-134\">system 42 light years from the Sun and lies at exactly the right distance from its star to allow liquid surface water.</span> It orbits well within the star\'s “habitable” or “Goldilocks” zone - the region where temperatures are neither too hot nor too cold to sustain life.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Professor Hugh Jones, from the University of Hertfordshire said: “The longer orbit of the new planet means that its climate and atmosphere may be just right to support life. <span class=\"answer-highlight highlight-2 hidden-highlight\" data-timestamp=\"1510019971641\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 123);\" data-highlighted=\"true\" data-qnumber=\"135\" id=\"hl-answer-135\">Just as Goldilocks liked her porridge to be neither too hot nor too cold but just right, this planet or indeed any moons that is has lie in an orbit comparable to Earth</span>, increasing the probability of it being habitable.” The ‘super earth’ is one of six planets believed to circle the dwarf star HD 40307 in the constellation Pictor. All the others are located outside the habitable zone, too close to their parent star to support liquid water.</span></span></span></p>\n\n                                \n                                \n                                \n                                ', NULL, '<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b><i>1. Why is it thought that the planet may be a