-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b><i>2. Which statement is true of the &ldquo;Goldilocks&rdquo; zone?</i></b></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>A</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-2 \" data-qnumber=\"135\" name=\"question-2\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"A\" /> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">It is the region of a planet which has a habitable climate.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>B</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-2 \" data-qnumber=\"135\" name=\"question-2\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"B\" /> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">It refers to a zone which is too close to the parent star.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>C</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-2 \" data-qnumber=\"135\" name=\"question-2\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"C\" /> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">It refers to a planet with several moons and a long orbit.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>D</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-2 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"135\" name=\"question-2\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"D\" /> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\"