span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>B</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-3 \" data-qnumber=\"142\" name=\"question-3\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"B\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span courier=\"\" new=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">being taken for granted </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>C</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-3 \" data-qnumber=\"142\" name=\"question-3\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"C\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span courier=\"\" new=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">the prime necessity. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>D</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-3 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"142\" name=\"question-3\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"D\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span courier=\"\" new=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">closely linked with shelter</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><div class=\"explain-area explain-3 explain-area-142\" data-qnumber=\"142\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"6\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 3 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">D</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-142\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-142\" data-qnumber=\"142\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"6\" onclick=\"showExplanation(142,3)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Fire </strong></span>is described as:</p>\n\n			<p>D: closely <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>linked with shelter</strong></span>.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>The need for <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>fire </strong></span>is <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>closely linked</strong></span>. (with shelter - that is mentionted in previous sentence)</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>The answer for this question can be found in the last sentence of second paragraph.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span courier=\"\" new=\"\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">4. According to the passage, which of the following statements is TRUE </span></span></span></b></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>A</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-4 \" data-qnumber=\"143\" name=\"question-4\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"A\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span courier=\"\" new=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">Exposure to wind not dangerous in mild climates, </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>B</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-4 \" data-qnumber=\"143\" name=\"question-4\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"B\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span courier=\"\" new=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">People may die quickly in the water of polar regions. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>C</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-4 \" data-qnumber=\"143\" name=\"question-4\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"C\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span courier=\"\" new=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">Looking for food is the first thing to do mast of the time. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>D</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-4 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"143\" name=\"question-4\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"D\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" times=\"\">Survivors after a flood won \'t need water for drinking.</span></span></span></span><div class=\"explain-area explain-4 explain-area-143\" data-qnumber=\"143\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"6\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 4 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">B</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-143\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-143\" data-qnumber=\"143\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"6\" onclick=\"showExplanation(143,4)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>B: People may <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>die</strong></span> <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>quickly </strong></span>in the<span style=\"color:#2980b9;\"><strong> water of polar regions</strong></span>.</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>death </strong></span>comes <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>in only minutes</strong></span> in the <span style=\"color:#2980b9;\"><strong>icy waters of the poles</strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>A is wrong, based on the second paragraph, exposure to wind can be fatal.</p>\n\n<p>C is wrong because in the third sentence of paragraph 2, we can see that: Food is rarely the first priority (rarely means not often)</p>\n\n<p>D is wrong, based on the information in the third paragraph: water is always universally important.</p>\n\n<p>B is the correct answer, you can find this information in the first highlighted sentence of second paragraph.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\">&nbsp;</p>\n', 4, 5, 6, 3, 1, '2017-11-06 15:13:58', '2017-11-15 15:24:25');
