tinent had the second-warmest, not the warmest.</p>\n\n<p>So, this statement is False.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n	<li style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-2 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"154\" name=\"question-2\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"TRUE\">TRUE</option><option value=\"FALSE\">FALSE</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">The temperature is rising due to the increased level of carbon dioxide in the atmosphere</span></span></span></li><div class=\"explain-area explain-2 explain-area-154\" data-qnumber=\"154\" data-qorder=\"2\" data-type-question=\"7\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 2 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">TRUE</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-154\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-154\" data-qnumber=\"154\" data-qorder=\"2\" data-type-question=\"7\" onclick=\"showExplanation(154,2)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>The <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>temperature is rising</strong></span> due to the <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>increased level of carbon dioxide in the atmosphere</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>While&nbsp;the impact of <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>increased levels of carbon dioxide in the atmosphere</strong></span> is a <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>key driver of rising temperatures...</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This information is quite clear in the first sentence of second paragraph.</p>\n\n<p>This paragraph indicates two main reasons for increasing temperatures are carbon dioxide and El Nino.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n	<li style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-3 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"155\" name=\"question-3\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"TRUE\">TRUE</option><option value=\"FALSE\">FALSE</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">2015 might be the hottest year in the history.</span></span></span></li><div class=\"explain-area explain-3 explain-area-155\" data-qnumber=\"155\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"7\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 3 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">TRUE</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-155\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-155\" data-qnumber=\"155\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"7\" onclick=\"showExplanation(155,3)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>2015 </strong></span>might be the <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>hottest year</strong></span> <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>in the history.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>many experts believe that <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>2015 </strong></span>will be the <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>warmest year on record </strong></span>by some margin.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>It\'s quite easy to do this question, You just need to scan for \"2015\" in the passage. In the third paragraph, you can find the information (in highlighted sentence)</p>\n\n<p>So, this statement is TRUE.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n	<li style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-4 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"156\" name=\"question-4\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"TRUE\">TRUE</option><option value=\"FALSE\">FALSE</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Record warming was recorded in various seas, such as Black and Azov Sea.&nbsp; </span></span></span></li><div class=\"explain-area explain-4 explain-area-156\" data-qnumber=\"156\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"7\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 4 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">NOT GIVEN</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-156\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-156\" data-qnumber=\"156\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"7\" onclick=\"showExplanation(156,4)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Record warming was recorded in various seas, such as <span style=\"color:#d35400;\"><strong>Black and Azov Sea.&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>with record warming in large expanses of the <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Pacific and Indian Oceans&nbsp;</strong></span><strong>(Not mention about Black and Azov Sea)</strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>In fourth paragrpah, it provides the information of the recording in Pacific and Indian Oceans, however, there is no information about Black and Azov Sea.</p>\n\n<p>This statement is clearly Not Given</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n	<li style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-5 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"157\" name=\"question-5\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"TRUE\">TRUE</option><option value=\"FALSE\">FALSE</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">The year 2015 might very well consist of a number of very warm months.</span></span></span></li><div class=\"explain-area explain-5 explain-area-157\" data-qnumber=\"157\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"7\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 5 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">TRUE</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-157\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-157\" data-qnumber=\"157\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"7\" onclick=\"showExplanation(157,5)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>The year 2015 <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>might </strong></span>very well consist of a number of <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>very warm months.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>...means <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>there is the&nbsp;potential</strong></span> to see some <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>very warm months </strong></span>throughout this year - as the new figures for July appear to show.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>For this statement, we can find the information in the last paragraph. In this paragraph, author mentions: there is the potential (means might...)</p>\n\n<p>This statement is true.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n</ol>\n', 5, 1, 7, 3, 1, '2017-11-07 09:12:10', '2017-11-15 15:45:49');
