pan></span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>TRUE &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </b>If the statement is true</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>FALSE &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </b>If the statement is false</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>NOT GIVEN &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </b>If the information is not given in the passage</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">1. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-1 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"168\" name=\"question-1\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"TRUE\">TRUE</option><option value=\"FALSE\">FALSE</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Knowing our feelings about stress can explain what causes the stress.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-1 explain-area-168\" data-qnumber=\"168\" data-qorder=\"1\" data-type-question=\"7\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 1 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">FALSE</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-168\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-168\" data-qnumber=\"168\" data-qorder=\"1\" data-type-question=\"7\" onclick=\"showExplanation(168,1)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Knowing our feelings about stress</strong></span> <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\"><strong>can explain</strong></span> what causes the stress. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>But <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>knowing how we feel when we experience stress</strong></span> <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:#ecf0f1;\">does not explain it</span></strong></span>; nor does it tell us what causes it.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>The last sentence of second paragraph expalins that knowing what we exprerience stress can not explain about stress.</p>\n\n<p>So, this statement is False</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">2. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-2 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"169\" name=\"question-2\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"TRUE\">TRUE</option><option value=\"FALSE\">FALSE</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Bothersome noises are more likely to cause stress than a poor test performance.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-2 explain-area-169\" data-qnumber=\"169\" data-qorder=\"2\" data-type-question=\"7\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 2 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">NOT GIVEN</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-169\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-169\" data-qnumber=\"169\" data-qorder=\"2\" data-type-question=\"7\" onclick=\"showExplanation(169,2)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>Bothersome noises</strong></span> <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:#ecf0f1;\">are more likely to cause stress</span></strong></span> than <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>a poor test performance</strong></span>.</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>A deadline, <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>a poor test performance</strong></span>, or <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>bothersome noises</strong></span> all may be thought of as stressors.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>There is <strong>no comparison</strong> between poor test performance and bothersome noises in this paragraph.</p>\n\n<p>So, this statement is Not Given</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">3. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-3 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"170\" name=\"question-3\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"TRUE\">TRUE</option><option value=\"FALSE\">FALSE</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Negative events cause more stress than positive ones do.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-3 explain-area-170\" data-qnumber=\"170\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"7\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 3 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">NOT GIVEN</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-170\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-170\" data-qnumber=\"170\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"7\" onclick=\"showExplanation(170,3)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Negative events</strong></span> cause <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:#ecf0f1;\">more stress </span></strong></span>than <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>positive ones</strong></span> do.</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Stress, then, can be caused by both <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>negative and positive events&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>Again, there is no comparison between negative events and positive invents in ways of creating stress.</p>\n\n<p>So, this statement is Not Given</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">4. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-4 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"171\" name=\"question-4\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"TRUE\">TRUE</option><option value=\"FALSE\">FALSE</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Sometimes whether an event is negative or not is based on a personal decision.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-4 explain-area-171\" data-qnumber=\"171\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"7\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 4 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">TRUE</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-171\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-171\" data-qnumber=\"171\" data-qorder=\"4\" data-type-question=\"7\" onclick=\"showExplanation(171,4)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Sometimes whether an <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>event is negative or not </strong></span>is <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>based on</strong></span> a <span style=\"color:#2980b9;\"><strong>personal decision.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Of course, whether <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>an event is thought of as positive or negative is</strong></span>, in some ways, <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>a matter of </strong></span><span style=\"color:#2980b9;\"><strong>personal choice.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>In highlighted sentence, we can find information for this statement.</p>\n\n<p>A matter of personal choice means personal decision. So, this statement is True</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">5. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-5 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"172\" name=\"question-5\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"TRUE\">TRUE</option><option value=\"FALSE\">FALSE</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Whether an event is considered stressful may be determined by the way people interpret it.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-5 explain-area-172\" data-qnumber=\"172\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"7\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 5 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">TRUE</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-172\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-172\" data-qnumber=\"172\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"7\" onclick=\"showExplanation(172,5)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Whether an event is considered stressful</strong></span> may be determined by the <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>way people interpret it.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>In sum, it is <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>the way people interpret </strong></span>an event that makes it <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>stressful or not stressful.&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>The first sentence of fifth paragraph provides this information.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">6. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-6 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"173\" name=\"question-6\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"TRUE\">TRUE</option><option value=\"FALSE\">FALSE</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">Sometimes those circumstances that are not threatening to us are also stressful.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-6 explain-area-173\" data-qnumber=\"173\" data-qorder=\"6\" data-type-question=\"7\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 6 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">FALSE</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-173\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-173\" data-qnumber=\"173\" data-qorder=\"6\" data-type-question=\"7\" onclick=\"showExplanation(173,6)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Sometimes those circumstances that <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>are not threatening to us</strong></span> <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\"><strong>are also stressful.</strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Circumstances that bring a threat or challenge to a person’s sense of well-being produce stress. <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Those that do not threaten</strong></span> or challenge us <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:#ecf0f1;\">are NOT&nbsp;stressful.</span></strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>The answer can be found in last sentence of sixth paragraph. This statement will be true if it said that: sometimes those circumstances that are not threatening to us <strong>ARE NOT STREESFUL</strong></p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">7. </span></span></span><select class=\"question-quiz question-select question-7 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"174\" name=\"question-7\" disabled=\"disabled\"><option value=\"\"></option><option value=\"TRUE\">TRUE</option><option value=\"FALSE\">FALSE</option><option value=\"NOT GIVEN\">NOT GIVEN</option></select> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">An event or situation may not always be a stressor.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-7 explain-area-174\" data-qnumber=\"174\" data-qorder=\"7\" data-type-question=\"7\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 7 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">TRUE</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-174\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-174\" data-qnumber=\"174\" data-qorder=\"7\" data-type-question=\"7\" onclick=\"showExplanation(174,7)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>An event or situation</strong></span> <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>may not always be a stressor.&nbsp; &nbsp; </strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>In addition, <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>the things</strong></span> that cause us stress today <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>may not cause us stress at another time. </strong></span>And the opposite is true: <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>things </strong></span>that <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>once caused no stress may now be stressful.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>Last paragraph expalins this idea quite clearly.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n', 7, 4, 7, 3, 1, '2017-11-07 11:10:45', '2017-11-15 16:17:39');
