</b>…Which of the artefacts mentioned are the oldest?&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></span><span class=\"label-input key-label\"><strong>1</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-input question-1 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"256\" name=\"question-1\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"text\" disabled=\"disabled\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-1 explain-area-256\" data-qnumber=\"256\" data-qorder=\"1\" data-type-question=\"11\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 1 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">(ochre) engravings/ (the) engravings</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-256\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-256\" data-qnumber=\"256\" data-qorder=\"1\" data-type-question=\"11\" onclick=\"showExplanation(256,1)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table class=\"explanation-table-custom\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Keyword: artefacts, oldest. ------------ In highlighted sentences, you can find out that there are three factors of artefacts are mention, including beads, bone tools, engravings. In comparison with those factors, engravings are the oldest (last sentence of first paragraph)</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>2</b>…When was the material Henshilwood found originally made?&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span><span class=\"label-input key-label\"><strong>2</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-input question-2 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"257\" name=\"question-2\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"text\" disabled=\"disabled\"></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-2 explain-area-257\" data-qnumber=\"257\" data-qorder=\"2\" data-type-question=\"11\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 2 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">100000 years ago</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-257\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-257\" data-qnumber=\"257\" data-qorder=\"2\" data-type-question=\"11\" onclick=\"showExplanation(257,2)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table class=\"explanation-table-custom\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>keyword: Henshilwood, originally. This question ask about time (when), so, scan for number of years is a good choice. --------- Scan for keyword, we can find the information about Henshilwood is found on second paragraph. Henshilwood discovered (found) a mixture - dates back to 100,000 years ago. So, answer for this question is 100,000 years ago</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>3</b>…What two common materials did ancient humans use to obtain their ochre?&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span><span class=\"label-input key-label\"><strong>3</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-input question-3 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"258\" name=\"question-3\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"text\" disabled=\"disabled\"></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-3 explain-area-258\" data-qnumber=\"258\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"11\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 3 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">earth or rock</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-258\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-258\" data-qnumber=\"258\" data-qorder=\"3\" data-type-question=\"11\" onclick=\"showExplanation(258,3)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table class=\"explanation-table-custom\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Keyword: two common materials ------------ In highlighted sentence, we can see that Ochre is a term used to describe a piece of earth or rock. It means that, Ochre is made by earth or rock. So, earth or rock is the correct answer.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>4</b>…What did the ancient people use to kee