ion</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-261\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-261\" data-qnumber=\"261\" data-qorder=\"6\" data-type-question=\"11\" onclick=\"showExplanation(261,6)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table class=\"explanation-table-custom\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>In highlighted sentence, we can find out that they use ochre for skin decoration and skin protection.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n', 6, 3, 11, 3, 1, '2017-11-10 13:41:46', '2017-11-14 17:09:20');
