n you answer this question, you need to find out it in paragraph 2. In highlighted sentence, we can see that they mention about time - 2 years. So, answer for this question is two years.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">5... Which languages are given as an example of what can benefit volunteers?&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span class=\"label-input key-label\"><strong>5</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-input question-5 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"266\" name=\"question-5\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"text\" disabled=\"disabled\"></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-5 explain-area-266\" data-qnumber=\"266\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"11\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 5 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">French and Spanish</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-266\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-266\" data-qnumber=\"266\" data-qorder=\"5\" data-type-question=\"11\" onclick=\"showExplanation(266,5)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table class=\"explanation-table-custom\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Those information can be found in last sentence of this passage.</p>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 10pt\">&nbsp;</p>\n', 5, 4, 11, 3, 1, '2