s=\"\">avoid building high-risk structures such as dams.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>D</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-9 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"388\" name=\"question-9\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"D\" disabled=\"disabled\"> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\">often concentrate too much on certain risk zones.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"explain-area explain-9 explain-area-388\" data-qnumber=\"388\" data-qorder=\"9\" data-type-question=\"3\"><div class=\"show-answer\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-show-answer\">Answer 9 <div class=\"badge badge-pill key-answer\">D</div></button><div class=\"explain-show\" id=\"explain-388\"> <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-show-explanation show-explanation-388\" data-qnumber=\"388\" data-qorder=\"9\" data-type-question=\"3\" onclick=\"showExplanation(388,9)\"><i class=\"fa fa-key\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Explanation</button><div class=\"hidden explanation\"><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n</div></div></div></div>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span new=\"\" roman=\"\" style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\"><b>10. One of the factors that led to the high death toll in Kobe was</b></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label