ot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">encourage their children to play more sports.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>B</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-7 \" data-qnumber=\"396\" name=\"question-7\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"B\" /> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">bring up their children well.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>C</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-7 \" data-qnumber=\"396\" name=\"question-7\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"C\" /> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">care about the environment.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>D</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-7 last-option\" data-qnumber=\"396\" name=\"question-7\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"D\" /> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">use their cars wherever possible.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><b>8. In some areas of Germany,</b></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 10pt\"><span class=\"label-radio key-label\"><strong>A</strong></span> <input class=\"question-quiz question-radio question-8 \" data-qnumber=\"397\" name=\"question-8\" onclick=\"bitest(this)\" type=\"radio\" value=\"A\" /> <span style=\"font-size:13pt\"><span style=\"line-heig