(1222, 2, 1, 4, 8, 'v', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<caption>Keywords Table</caption>\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Words in Question</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Similar words in passage</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Who </strong></span>is likely to <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>get </strong></span>cancer?&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>What personality traits</strong></span> <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>make up</strong></span> the cancer-prone personality?</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>In paragraph A, author talks about cancer-prone personality, and in this paragraph, It mentions about the personality traits. It means that people who have those traits tend to be cancer. v - is the correct answer</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 09:16:21', '2017-11-15 09:16:21'),
(1223, 2, 1, 4, 9, 'ii', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<caption>Keyword Table</caption>\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Words in Question</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Similar words in passage</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Nothing to see <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>on the surface&nbsp; </strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Do not show stress <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>outwardly</strong></span>. Instead,&nbsp;they keep their emotions <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>bottled inside</strong></span>.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>In highlighted sentences, we can see that ii is the correct answer. &quot;outwardly&quot; means outsite.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 09:16:21', '2017-11-15 09:16:21'),
(1224, 2, 1, 4, 10, 'i', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<caption>Keyword Table</caption>\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Words in Question</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Similar words in passage</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#d35400;\"><strong>Get angry</strong></span>, <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>live longer&nbsp;</strong></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>These patients get sick faster and they <span style=\"color:#e74c3c;\"><strong>die sooner</strong></span> than people who <span style=\"color:#d35400;\"><strong>became angry</strong></span> at their cancer and fight the disease.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This paragraph explains about some traits that help vitims of cancer recover from their illness. The last sentence talk about becoming angry at victim&#39;s cancer themeself will help live longer. So, <strong>heading i</strong> is the right answer</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 09:16:21', '2017-11-15 09:16:21'),
(1225, 2, 1, 4, 11, 'iv', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Which one <strong>causes</strong> which? &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>getting <strong>cancer may cause</strong> people to develop a <strong>cancer-prone personality.</strong></p>\n\n			<p>there is no proof that having a <strong>cancer-prone personality causes cancer.</strong></p>\n\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>this paragraph clearly talks about the relationship of cancer-prone personality and cancer, which one causes which?</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>heading iv</strong> is the correct answer</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 09:16:21', '2017-11-15 09:16:21'),
(1230, 4, 1, 4, 18, 'iii', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>&nbsp;Urban planning has a <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>long</strong></span> and <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>varied history</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>....is an <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>ancient one</strong></span></p>\n\n			<p>....<span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>various planned</strong></span> communities (both theoretical and actual) were conceived</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>First sentence is the topic sentence of this paragraph. It indicates that urban planning happend in a very long time ago (acient one).</p>\n\n<p>In next supporting sentences, they give information about history of many planned communities (varied). So, <strong>heading iii</strong> is the correct answer.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 09:47:33', '2017-11-15 09:47:33'),
(1231, 4, 1, 4, 19, 'v', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>The <span style=\"color:#d35400;\"><strong>background </strong></span>to one <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>particular planned community&nbsp; </strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>...as a <span style=\"color:#d35400;\"><strong>reaction to the pollution and crowding of the Industrial Revolution</strong></span></p>\n\n			<p>One of the most important <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>planned city concepts</strong></span>, the <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Garden City</strong></span></p>\n\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This paragraph explains the progress of creating Gargen City. All sentences of this paragraph give information about the way garden city created - this could be seen in heading v - background to one particular planned community - Garden city.</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>heading v</strong> is the correct answer.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 09:47:33', '2017-11-15 09:47:33'),
(1232, 4, 1, 4, 20, 'vii', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>An urban plan to <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>reduce traffic&nbsp; </strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>...designed so that the residents would<span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong> not require automobiles</strong></span></p>\n\n			<p>...which <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>shared 23 acres of commonly held parkland</strong></span>.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>In highlighted sentences, we can see that this paragraph talks about the resident that would not require automobiles. Heading vii - An urban plan to reduce traffic - is the only heading that mention about traffic - automobiles.</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>Heading vii</strong> is the correct answer.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 09:47:33', '2017-11-15 09:47:33'),
(1233, 4, 1, 4, 21, 'iv', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Financial problems</strong></span> helped <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>spread an urban planning concept</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>...following the <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>stock market crash</strong></span> of 1929...</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>In the first sentence of this paragraph, it talks about the stock market crash - means financial problems - and then, it leads to the <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>creation of three towns. </strong></span></p>\n\n<p><strong>Heading iv</strong> is the correct answer because it mentions all about the financial crisis and the creation of three towns (spread an urban planning concept)</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 09:47:33', '2017-11-15 09:47:33'),
(1234, 5, 1, 4, 22, 'vii', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Free services</strong></span> <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>for everyone&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>It charges <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>no fee for its services</strong></span></p>\n\n			<p>These books or other materials may be borrowed, or taken out for a speciﬁc time, <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>by anyone in the community</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This paragraph is about the way people borrowed books without any fee - it is totally free.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Heading vii</strong> is the correct answer.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:03:35', '2017-11-15 10:03:35'),
(1235, 5, 1, 4, 23, 'i', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Financial support</strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>...Public libraries are usually <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>tax-supported</strong></span>...</p>\n\n			<p>...from <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>money </strong></span>that has been <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>donated</strong></span></p>\n\n			<p>...some that receive part of their money&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>from taxes and part from gifts</strong></span>.</p>\n\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>The whole paragraph describes the way the public library get money - financial support.</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>heading i </strong>is the correct answer.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:03:35', '2017-11-15 10:03:35'),
(1236, 5, 1, 4, 24, 'viii', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>A <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\">wide </span><span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>Variety&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Not only </strong></span>are the <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>shapes </strong></span>and <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>sizes </strong></span>of the buildings different, but so are the <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>number of books</strong></span> and <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>other materials in each</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This paragraph is about the difference of many public libraries. Just take a look at all the headings, we only find heaidng viii mentions the wide variety of public library.</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>heading viii</strong> is the correct answer.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:03:35', '2017-11-15 10:03:35'),
(1237, 5, 1, 4, 25, 'ix', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Similar ways</strong></span> to <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>arrange books&nbsp;</strong></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Most public libraries, however,&nbsp; <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>arrange their books </strong></span>and other materials in <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>similar way</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>It is clear that this paragraph describes about the similar way that many public library use to arrange their books. Just read the highlighted sentences, you can find such ways.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:03:35', '2017-11-15 10:03:35'),
(1238, 5, 1, 4, 26, 'vi', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Certain books </strong></span><span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>stay in the library&nbsp;</strong></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>look something up in a certain <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>basic information book.</strong></span>&nbsp;Thus <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>reference books</strong></span>, which are rarely read cover to cover, are <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>put in a special place</strong></span> in the library</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This paragraph concerns reference books, which are an certain kind of books that cannot be taken out of the library</p>\n\n<p><strong>Heading vi</strong> is the correct heading for this paragraph.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:03:35', '2017-11-15 10:03:35'),
(1239, 5, 1, 4, 27, 'ii', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\">Local decisions</span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>It would depend on what the <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\">people in that city had indicated they found useful</span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>The last question of this paragraph leads us to the heading ii. This paragraph can be disturbed by heading ix - the way books were arranged, however, this paragraph describes nothing about &quot;similary ways&quot; - there is no comparison here.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:03:35', '2017-11-15 10:03:35'),
(1240, 5, 1, 4, 28, 'iii', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Inﬂuence </strong></span>of <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>people&#39;s interests&nbsp; </strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>These holdings almost always <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>reﬂect </strong></span>the <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>community&rsquo;s special interests</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>The first two sentences give the main idea of this paragraph. &quot;reflect the community&#39;s interests&quot; equal to &quot;influence of poeple&#39;s interetss&quot;. So, heading iii is the correct answer.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:03:35', '2017-11-15 10:03:35'),
(1241, 6, 1, 4, 29, 'vii', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Importance </strong></span>of <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>female education &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>The beneﬁts </strong></span>of <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>educating girls</strong></span> are <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>enormous</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>The first sentence of this paragraph is the topic sentence. The whole paragraph indicates the benifits of female education.</p>\n\n<p>So,<strong> heading vii</strong> is the right answer.</p>\n\n<p>Heading v is not the right one, because this paragraph does not mention about any problems.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:35:36', '2017-11-15 10:35:36'),
(1242, 6, 1, 4, 30, 'viii', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Educating girls means <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>smaller families&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>The educational level achieved by women has the most powerful <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>inﬂuence on family size</strong></span></p>\n\n			<p>Educating girls is three times more likely than educating boys to <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>lower family size </strong></span></p>\n\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>...Fewer children</strong></span> than less educated ones</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>It is clear that this paragraph talks about family size - educated girls tend to have smaller family size (fewer children).</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>heading viii </strong>is the correct answer.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:35:36', '2017-11-15 10:35:36'),
(1243, 6, 1, 4, 31, 'iv', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Now<span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong> parents must pay&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>...putting more <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>responsibility on families for financing </strong></span>education</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This paragraph describes the costs that families have to pay for their children in education. In highlighted sentences, you can see that now government cut their spending on education, as the result, families must pay for that.</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>heading iv</strong> is the correct answer.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:35:36', '2017-11-15 10:35:36'),
(1244, 6, 1, 4, 32, 'iii', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Educational problems </strong></span>of <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>girls</strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Parents may see<span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong> limited economic beneﬁts</strong></span> in educating <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>daughters</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>First sentence of this paragraph is the topic sentence. This paragraph indicates the disadvantages of educating girls in comparison with boys.</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>heading iii </strong>is the correct answer</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:35:36', '2017-11-15 10:35:36'),
(1245, 6, 1, 4, 33, 'i', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>How </strong></span>to <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>get more girls into school&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Efforts to<span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong> increase female enrolment levels</strong></span>..</p>\n\n			<p><span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>Building more schools</strong></span>...</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This paragraph describes some ways to increase more girls in schools such as building mor shools, using existing resources for education (in poor countries)...</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>heading i</strong> is the correct answer.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:35:36', '2017-11-15 10:35:36'),
(1246, 6, 1, 4, 34, 'v', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><strong><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\">Solving </span></strong>some <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>other problems&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>...can help to <strong><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\">overcome&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#e67e22;\">cultural barriers</span></strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>In highlighted sentences, you can see that this paragraph gives some solutions to solves other problems to encourage more girls in schools.</p>\n\n<p>Methods to solve other problems mentioned are:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>scholarships&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Flexible school schedules</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>So, <strong>heading v</strong> is the correct answer.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Heading i </strong>also can disturb you from find&nbsp;the correct answer for this section. However, heading i is more relevant for section E. So, heading v is the correct one.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:35:36', '2017-11-15 10:35:36'),
(1247, 6, 1, 4, 35, 'vi', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>Family planning </strong></span><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>plus schooling&nbsp; </strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Average <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>family size and child death rates are lowest,</strong></span> however, in countries that combine <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>strong family planning and health programmes</strong></span> with&nbsp; <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>levels of education for women.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This whole passage is about educating girls. So, in this last section, it mentions family planning services, in accordance with education for girls could bring many benefits.</p>\n\n<p>In this passage, Famlily planning plus schooling means family planning helps to get better&nbsp;education level for women in school</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>heading vi</strong> is the correct answer</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:35:36', '2017-11-15 10:35:36'),
(1248, 7, 1, 4, 36, 'iv', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Three Factors&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>...certain facts about&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>geography</strong></span>,<strong><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"> history</span></strong>, and <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>economics</strong></span></p>\n\n			<p>...<span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>these three</strong></span> will explain the huge growth of America&rsquo;s most famous city.<span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This paragraph is the introduction of New York, in comparison with Philadelphia and Boston. It indicates 3 factors that would be explained in this paragraph.</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>heading iv</strong> is the correct answer.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:52:44', '2017-11-15 10:52:44'),
(1249, 7, 1, 4, 37, 'iii', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Seaports&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>The map of the Northeast shows that four of the most heavily populated areas in this region <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>are around seaports</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This short paragraph is about seaport. So, <strong>heading ii</strong> is the correct answer.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:52:44', '2017-11-15 10:52:44'),
(1250, 7, 1, 4, 38, 'v', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Not just </strong></span>because of <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>where it is&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </strong></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>But cities like New York needed <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>more than</strong></span> <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>their geographical location </strong></span>in order to become great industrial centres.&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>In last 2 sentences, you can see the main point of this paragraph is that New York does not depend only on their place (geographical location).</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>Heading v</strong> is the correct answer.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:52:44', '2017-11-15 10:52:44'),
(1251, 7, 1, 4, 39, 'viii', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Further development</strong></span> of water transport&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Freight costs were cut to about one tenth</strong></span> of what they had been</p>\n\n			<p>...<span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>transportation routes on the Great Lakes were joined to routes on the Mississippi River.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>In previous paragraph, it describes canal shipping, and in this section, it all gives information about further development of using canal (You can see those further advantages in highlighted sentences)</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>heading viii</strong> is the correct answer</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:52:44', '2017-11-15 10:52:44'),
(1252, 7, 1, 4, 40, 'i', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>Then <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>came the train&nbsp;</strong></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>The <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>coming of the railroads</strong></span>&nbsp;made canal shipping less important,</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>It is clear that this short paragraph is about the comming of the train.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Heading i</strong> is correct heading for this section</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:52:44', '2017-11-15 10:52:44'),
(1253, 7, 1, 4, 41, 'ii', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Cheap fares </strong></span>from <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>Europe&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Passengers could come from <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>Europe </strong></span><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>very cheaply</strong></span> as a result.</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>Heading ii is the only heading suitable for this section. This short section gives information about the consequence of exprts from New York.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:52:44', '2017-11-15 10:52:44'),
(1254, 7, 1, 4, 42, 'vi', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Most popular </strong></span>place to <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>arrive&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>New York became the <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>greatest port </strong></span>for <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>receiving people from European countries</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>First sentence is the topic sentence of this paragraph. New York became the greatest place for people to come and stay. In following sentences, they give idea to support this topic sentence.</p>\n\n<p>So, <strong>heading vi</strong> is the correct answer.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 10:52:44', '2017-11-15 10:52:44'),
(1255, 10, 1, 5, 55, 'F', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>The areas with the highest proportion</strong></span> of<span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong> tourism related jobs.</strong></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>The top ten local areas</strong></span> for <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>tourism related employment</strong></span> in the UK, as a proportion of total employment...</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>Pragraph F gives information about top local areas, with have the highest proportion. So,paragrph&nbsp;F is the correct answer</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 11:18:26', '2017-11-15 11:18:26'),
(1256, 10, 1, 5, 56, 'D', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Areas </strong></span>with the <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>highest </strong></span>and <span style=\"color:#d35400;\"><strong>lowest</strong></span> percentage of <span style=\"color:#2980b9;\"><strong>tourism related jobs.&nbsp;</strong></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>In <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Torbay, Devon</strong></span>, for example, more than <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>15 per cent </strong></span>of all <span style=\"color:#2980b9;\"><strong>employment was in tourism and related industries,</strong></span> while in parts of the West Midlands the figure was <span style=\"color:#d35400;\"><strong>as low as 5 per cent.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>In the last sentence of paragraph D, we can see that it lists all the areas with specific highest (over 15%) and lowest (5%) percentage.</p>\n\n<p>This question is quite hard. Just take a look at the table in paragraph F, you can see that Torbay get the highest percentage and there is no area has the proportion lower thatn 5%, so Devon has the lowest percentage of tourism related jobs.</p>\n\n<p>Paragraph B only mentions about tourism-related jobs in London, so it is not the correct answer.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 11:18:26', '2017-11-15 11:18:26'),
(1257, 10, 1, 5, 57, 'E', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>Examples </strong></span>of tourism related jobs.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>Tourism related industries include<span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong> accommodation</strong></span>, the <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>food and beverage sector</strong></span>, <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>passenger transport, vehicle hire, travel agencies, cultural, recreation and sports activities, and also conference activities.</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>It is clear that E is the correct answer because it describes all tourism related jobs.</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 11:18:26', '2017-11-15 11:18:26'),
(1258, 10, 1, 5, 58, 'A', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>The area</strong></span> with the <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>largest number</strong></span> of tourism related jobs.</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>London </strong></span>has the <span style=\"color:#e67e22;\"><strong>largest number of jobs related</strong></span> to Great Britain&#39;s tourist industry</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This paragraph talks about London that has the largest number of job related to tourism industry</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 11:18:26', '2017-11-15 11:18:26'),
(1259, 10, 1, 5, 59, 'C', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"explanation-table-custom\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Words in question</td>\n			<td>Similar words in passage</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p>The <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>total number</strong></span> of people working in tourism related jobs in the UK.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>there were just under <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>three million people with jobs</strong></span> in tourism and tourism related industries in the UK &ndash; around <span style=\"color:#1abc9c;\"><strong>9 per cent of all employment</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This is the only paragraph talks about the sepicfic number of people working in tourism related jobs in UK</p>\n', 1, '2017-11-15 11:18:26', '2017-11-15 11:18:26');
